<% content_for :title, "About Andrew Clough - Clough for SC5" %>

<div style="background-color: #0F2044; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
  <div style="max-width: 1440px; margin-inline: auto; display: flex; font-size: 12px; min-height: 520px; padding-inline: 120px;">
    <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-basis: 0%; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; flex-shrink: 1; gap: 20px; justify-content: center; padding-bottom: 80px; padding-right: 60px; padding-top: 80px;">
      <div style="align-items: center; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
        <div style="background-color: #C8902A; box-sizing: border-box; flex-shrink: 0; height: 32px; width: 3px;"></div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #C8902A; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; line-height: 16px; text-transform: uppercase;">
          About Andrew
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 'Playfair Display', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 52px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; white-space: pre-wrap;">
        Built by District 5.<br />Running for District 5.
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px; max-width: 520px;">
        Andrew Clough is a husband, father, and Rock Hill native who has spent his career serving this community. He's running for Congress because District 5 deserves a voice that actually shows up.
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-top: 8px;">
        <div style="background-color: #C8902A; border-radius: 4px; box-sizing: border-box; padding-block: 14px; padding-inline: 28px;">
          <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.02em; line-height: 18px;">
            Join the Campaign
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3); border-radius: 4px; border-style: solid; border-width: 1.5px; box-sizing: border-box; padding-block: 14px; padding-inline: 28px;">
          <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 18px;">
            Read His Story
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
<div style="align-items: center; background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06); box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-shrink: 0; justify-content: center; width: 420px;">
    <%= image_tag 'andrew-cloughA.jpg', style: "width: 300px; height: 380px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 4px; border: 2px solid rgba(200, 144, 42, 0.3);" %>
  </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #FFFFFF; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
  <div style="max-width: 1440px; margin-inline: auto; display: flex; gap: 80px; padding-block: 80px; padding-inline: 120px;">
    <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-basis: 0%; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; flex-shrink: 1; gap: 32px;">
      <div style="align-items: center; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
        <div style="background-color: #C8902A; box-sizing: border-box; flex-shrink: 0; height: 28px; width: 3px;"></div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #C8902A; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; line-height: 16px; text-transform: uppercase;">
          His Story
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0F2044; font-family: 'Playfair Display', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
        A life rooted in this district
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6B7280; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
        Andrew Clough grew up in Rock Hill, went to school here, and built his family here. He's watched this district grow — and he's watched Washington ignore it. Textile mills closing. The VA clinic stretched thin. Young families leaving because they can't afford to stay.
      </div>
<div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6B7280; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
        He spent years in community service, understanding firsthand how decisions made in Washington play out on the streets of York County. He knows that the people of District 5 aren't looking for a career politician — they're looking for someone who will actually fight for them.
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6B7280; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
        Andrew is running as a Democrat because he believes in an economy that works for working people, healthcare that doesn't bankrupt families, and a government that tells the truth. He's not backed by PACs. He's backed by neighbors.
      </div>
    </div>
<div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-shrink: 0; gap: 24px; width: 360px;">
      <div style="background-color: #F9F8F6; border-left-color: #C8902A; border-left-style: solid; border-left-width: 4px; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; padding-block: 28px; padding-inline: 24px;">
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0F2044; font-family: 'Playfair Display', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
          "District 5 has been overlooked for too long. I'm running because I refuse to accept that as normal."
        </div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6B7280; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 16px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 16px;">
          — Andrew Clough
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="background-color: #F9F8F6; border-radius: 8px; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; padding-block: 28px; padding-inline: 24px;">
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #C8902A; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; line-height: 14px; text-transform: uppercase;">
          Fast Facts
        </div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;">
          <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #9CA3AF; display: inline-block; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 80px;">
              Home
            </div>
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #374151; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 18px;">
              Rock Hill, SC
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #9CA3AF; display: inline-block; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 80px;">
              Party
            </div>
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #374151; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 18px;">
              Democrat
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #9CA3AF; display: inline-block; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 80px;">
              District
            </div>
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #374151; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 18px;">
              SC-05
            </div>
          </div>
          <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #9CA3AF; display: inline-block; flex-shrink: 0; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; width: 80px;">
              Primary
            </div>
            <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #374151; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; line-height: 18px;">
              June 2026
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #F9F8F6; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
  <div style="max-width: 1440px; margin-inline: auto; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 48px; padding-block: 80px; padding-inline: 120px;">
    <div style="align-items: center; box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 12px;">
      <div style="background-color: #C8902A; box-sizing: border-box; flex-shrink: 0; height: 28px; width: 3px;"></div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #C8902A; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; line-height: 16px; text-transform: uppercase;">
        Values
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; gap: 32px;">
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-basis: 0%; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; flex-shrink: 1; gap: 12px;">
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0F2044; font-family: 'Playfair Display', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
          Community First
        </div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6B7280; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
          Every decision Andrew makes in Congress will start with one question: does this help the people of District 5? Not donors. Not party leadership. Neighbors.
        </div>
      </div>
<div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-basis: 0%; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; flex-shrink: 1; gap: 12px;">
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0F2044; font-family: 'Playfair Display', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
          Straight Talk
        </div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6B7280; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
          Andrew says what he means. No hedging, no spin. If he disagrees with something, he'll say so. District 5 has had enough of politicians who talk around every answer.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-basis: 0%; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; flex-shrink: 1; gap: 12px;">
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #0F2044; font-family: 'Playfair Display', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
          Show Up
        </div>
        <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #6B7280; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
          Being a congressman means being present. Town halls, school visits, coffee meetups — Andrew will be in the district regularly, not just at election time.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>  </div>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #0F2044; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box;">
  <div style="max-width: 1440px; margin-inline: auto; align-items: center; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding-block: 80px; padding-inline: 120px;">
    <div style="box-sizing: border-box; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; max-width: 560px;">
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #C8902A; display: inline-block; font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; line-height: 16px; text-transform: uppercase;">
        Get Involved
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #FFFFFF; font-family: 'Playfair Display', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
        This campaign runs on neighbors, not donors.
      </div>
      <div style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65); font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-top: 0px;">
